{"lastModified":1754989911144,"uri":"c::18121082131::vessel::9031d5a0-8953-11ee-b867-33f49d7a1d61","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia, Slovenia, Montenegro, East Mediterranean\n\nThe Princess shipyard unveiled its masterpiece, the luxury motor yacht Princess 62 \"SASSY\" in 2009. Since then, this maritime gem has been an epitome of opulence and nautical skills. with a recent refit in 2023 and continously 2024, SASSY not only maintains her regal allure but also embraced modernity in style and functionality. The spacious salon, with panoramic windows spanning fore to aft, invites abundant natural light, creating an open and airy ambiance. Interior is contemporary and neutral-toned, the lounge area at the aft boasts two generous sofas, a coffee table, and a state-of-the-art drop-down entertainment system. Forward, a raised formal dining table accommodates all guests, offering not just a meal but a feast for the eyes through the surrounding windows.\n\nThe aft deck, adjacent to the salon, offers partial shade and an alfresco dining option, creating a perfect spot for entertaining. The side decks elegantly wrap around the yacht, leading to a comfortable foredeck. The flybridge, features additional alfresco dining, seating, a removable bimini for shade, and a sunning area – the ideal setting to revel in the sun-drenched beauty of the adriatic. SASSY offers spacious accommodation for up to 8 charter guests in 4 guest cabins. the master suite, positioned amidships, is a sanctuary of luxury with a queen-size bed, large vertical hull windows, TV entertainment, vanity, and a sofa. The VIP cabin, forward and full beam, features a center-lined double bed. Two additional guest cabins, one with side-by-side twin beds and the other with upper and lower single beds, complete the accommodations, ensuring a comfortable and personalized experience for all aboard.","blueprint":{"name":"SASSY","images":["/media/media::image::c::18121082131::vessel::9031d5a0-8953